Package sailpoint.object

Class Question

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.Question
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
    public class Question
extends AbstractXmlObject
    An object representing a data value that needs to be requested, typically through interactive prompting. This is part of the ProvisioningProject model, used to represent account attributes that are required to complete a provisioning event.
